{"tid":225752,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"菲林DIY沖掃討論區","createTime":"2017-05-02T04:25:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T06:25:54.000Z","uid":107154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3e816cb36eddf2e3a6e678483947d188918f5354","tid":225752,"uid":107154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T04:25:37.000Z","msg":"最近因為想影啲私密題材 但菲林比人沖姐係會流出啲相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽講自己沖黑白菲林好簡單？<br />\n有暗袋就唔使暗房？<br />\n沖完係咪要有掃菲林嘅專用scaner？<br />\n<br />\n淘寶見到呢啲 想買黎試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/808n272.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F808n272.jpg&h=3b7155af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打識自己沖菲林？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求指救"},{"pid":"ceb10cd43fb277bc402e69a220841b7564bdcd6e","tid":225752,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T05:04:30.000Z","msg":"藥水响香港買<br />\n其餘既野( 黑袋，沖罐，量杯等可以响淘寶買 )<br />\n<br />\nscan 就要買部可以 scan  film 既 scanner"},{"pid":"249f3ebb1c4fa233fc89ba3fb6c17115c76c011a","tid":225752,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T05:06:08.000Z","msg":"沖罐老翻都無問題，我自己用緊老翻 ap 罐，用左咁多年都無事"},{"pid":"724a92fb6e3dde890761caef550eb31dcc8631b9","tid":225752,"uid":18111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T05:38:02.000Z","msg":"藥 可以用 Kodak HC-110 先, 易用又百搭.<br />\n買個針筒, 開藥時要用.<br />\n<br />\nscanner 認真唔好買canon. 實後悔, 過來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 貴少少買epson v700/v800"},{"pid":"f2e8282609508d02907c743973608a044f0c12e7","tid":225752,"uid":18111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T05:39:12.000Z","msg":"你寫一寫個checklist 先. 睇下有無野漏幫你執"},{"pid":"7fef27